Rating: 4
Just a follow up regarding flour type: Pillsbury AP bleached flour or any cake flour will give you a much better texture/crumb than unbleached AP flour. Unbleached AP results in a rather coarse and dense texture...too coarse for such a delicate cake. Also, half the recipe fills 4 mini-bread pans perfectly.

